# Copy to .env to opt into real data sources. Defaults (no .env) use local sample/mock data and
# a local embedding fallback: zero cost, no network calls. See
# docs/integration/AIRFLOW_PIPELINE_PLAN.md for the security boundary this respects.

EMBEDDING_PROVIDER=local
# EMBEDDING_PROVIDER=openai
# OPENAI_API_KEY=

JOB_DATA_SOURCE=sample
# JOB_DATA_SOURCE=work24
# WORK24_API_KEY=
# Real jobs must come from work24.go.kr's public Open API only (register at
# https://www.work24.go.kr/cm/e/a/0110/selectOpenApiSvcInfo.do). Never point this pipeline at
# JobKorea or another job board's live site directly — see AIRFLOW_PIPELINE_PLAN.md HOLD.
